quran[14{c,v,t}:
19,12,""" ae yahya! kitaab Ellahi ko mazboot thaam le"" hum ne ussay bachpan hi mein"" hukum"" se nawaza"
19,13,aur apni taraf se is ko naram dili aur pakizgee ataa ki aur woh bara parhaizgaar
19,14,aur apne walidain ka haq shanaas tha woh jabbar nah tha aur nah nafarman
19,15,salam uss par jis roz ke woh peda howa aur jis din woh marey aur jis roz woh zindah kar ke uthaya jaye
19,16,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, is kitaab mein maryam ka haal bayan karo, jabkay woh apne logon se allag ho kar Sharqi janib gosha nasheen ho gayi thi"
19,17,aur parda daal kar unn se choup baithi thi is haalat mein hum ne is ke paas apni rooh ko ( yani farishtay ko ) bheja aur woh is ke samnay aik poooray ensaan ki shakal mein namodaar ho gaya
19,18,"maryam yakayak bol uthi ke"" agar to koi khuda taras aadmi hai to mein tujh se rehman ki panah maangti hon """
19,19,"uss ne kaha"" mein to tairay rab ka Farstada hon aur is liye bheja gaya hon ke tujhe aik pakeeza larka dun """
19,20,"maryam ne kaha"" mere haan kaisay larka hoga jabkay mujhe kisi bashar ne chuva taq nahi hai aur mein koi badkaar aurat nahi hon """
19,21,"farishtay ne kaha"" aisa hi hoga, tera rab farmata hai ke aisa karna mere liye bohat aasaan hai aur hum yeh is liye karen ge ke uss larke ko logon ke liye aik nishani banayen aur apni taraf se aik rehmat aur yeh kaam ho kar rehna hai """
19,22,maryam ko is bachay ka hamal reh gaya aur woh is hamal ko liye hue aik door ke maqam par chali gayi
19,23,"phir zichgi ki takleef ne ussay aik khajoor ke darakht ke neechay pouncha diya woh kehnay lagi"" kash mein is se pehlay hi mar jati aur mera naam o nishaan nah rehta """
19,24,"farishtay ne painti se is ko pukaar kar kaha"" gham ne kar tairay rab ne tairay neechay aik chashma rawan kar diya hai"
19,25,"aur to zara iss darakht ke tanay ko hila, tairay oopar tar o taaza khjorin tapak parrin gi"
